---

<Layout
  title="Digital Smile Design - LUMIA Specialized Dentistry"
  description="Complete smile transformation with advanced 3D technology. Personalized Digital Smile Design at LUMIA. Predictable and natural results."
  lang={lang}
  keywords="smile design Colombia, dental veneers, smile makeover, cosmetic dentistry, perfect smile"
>
  <Header />

  <main class="pt-20">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section
      class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-gold to-primary-gold-dark text-white relative overflow-hidden"
    >
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20"></div>
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <div
