              >
                Schedule Consultation
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://wa.me/573000000000"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-primary-gold font-bold rounded-lg transition-all duration-300"
              >
                <svg
                  class="mr-2 w-5 h-5"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
